snippet.title: Salty Hounds - Game Trailer 2022
snippet.description:
"Salty Hounds", the Open-World Bodyguard Dating RPG 💕

Twitter : https://twitter.com/toppingpalette

#Datingsim #Pixel #Openworld #rpg #switch #PC #Otome #VA 

__________ Love interests & Korean Voice Actors:

Noru (VA: Ryu Seunggon, i.e. Haikyuu!! - Koshi Sugawara, One Punch Man - Stinger, Genshin - Thoma, League of Legends - Taric)

Taemin (VA: Shim Gyuhyuk, i.e. Genshin Impact- Xiao, Marvel MCU - Peter Parker, Haikyuu!! - Kageyama Tobio, My Hero Academia - Midoriya Izuku, MM - Yoosung)

Seha (VA: Son Suho, i.e. Overwatch - Daehyun Park, Detective Conan - Yuya Kazami, Library of Ruina - Roland)

Yujin (VA: Jang Sungho, i.e. Yu-Gi-Oh! - Kaiba, My Hero Academia - Stain, Hunter x Hunter - Hisoka, Star Wars ~The Empire Strikes Back ~ - Lorth Needa)

Junho  (VA: Lee Juchang, i.e. Detective Conan - Akai Shuichi, Gintama - Hijikata Toshiro, Haikyuu!! - Iwaizumi Hajime, Darker Than Black - Hei)
